Update: Regarding this dataset:
covid19india.org has stopped operations of data collection since October 31st , 2021.
For more info please read this [blog post](https://blog.covid19india.org/2021/08/07/end/) where they had cited their reasons.
Meanwhile if I find another source i will add that in another dataset .
This Dataset is Sourced from https://www.covid19india.org/ 
Read their [About](https://www.covid19india.org/about) Page For More details on how they collected this information.
